Catalogued as the 400th Layer of the+Abyss, Woeful Escarand is a place where Nalfeshnee Lords of Woe sit in judgement over Petitioners and tanar'ri alike. Those they judge may be promoted, demoted, or cast into the Pit of Flame beneath the Mountain of Woe.
Sources: Planes of Chaos, Hellbound, Uncaged, Fiendish Codex: The Lost Annals